KMFDMADAW182A.name: KMFDM BRUTE A Drug Against War a #182
description: The first in a trilogy of a lesbian revenge artworks, ADAW
features an armed and enraged woman emerging from a car; machine
pistol primed for action. Firearms played a big part in my work
during this period and the silenced Ingrams Mac 10 really added
to the thrust of the image. The illustration was one of many
KMFDM covers that were animated for the 1993 video - BRUTE!
